      • ApiAggregator

        public ApiAggregator(String name,
                     Map<String,ApiProvider> ifaceMap,
                     boolean deployIntrospectionServices)
        Constructor. Optionally can deploy a set of introspection services which expose the introspection API of the provider through invoke(String, String, DataValue, ExecutionContext, AsyncHandle).
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the API aggregator if missing, AGGREGATOR_DEFAULT_NAME will be used
        ifaceMap - map of service id to provider which handles that service
        deployIntrospectionServices - whether to automatically deploy introspection services
